1) install the rpm-build package
 # yum --disablerepo="*" --enablerepo="rhel7.3" search all rpm-build
 # ls /root/rpmbuild/
   BUILD  RPMS  SOURCES  SPECS  SRPMS
2) create spec file in SPECS directory 
3) create **.tar.gz in SOURCES directory
4) rpmbuild -ba  ../SPECS/*.spec
-REF
https://www.thegeekstuff.com/2015/02/rpm-build-package-example/
